name: Stand With Crypto Fund
description: A charity memecoin on Base donating 100% of trading fees to the Stand With Crypto movement. Stand With Crypto Fund (SWC) is a charity-focused token on the Base blockchain designed to support the Stand With Crypto initiative. Every transaction incurs a 5% automated tax, with 100% of collected funds sent directly to the official Stand With Crypto donation wallet. SWC operates with no developer tax or private allocations.
